00:01:38.839 --> 00:01:41.919
in his word with regard to the subject of tongues,

00:01:41.919 --> 00:01:45.279
and yet there's so much confusion in our world

00:01:45.279 --> 00:01:47.400
with regard to tongues.

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:50.760
